    "GPT 3.5 vs original; P<0.001 GPT 3.5 vs GPT 4) (Table 5).",
    "However, it should be noted that the readability data was available for 45 out of the 62 abstracts initially selected for this study due to incomplete evaluations in the assessment process.",
